From: Jeehyun Lee <jeehyun.lee@lge.com>
Date: Wed, 5 Nov 2025 10:04:36 +0900
Subject: id3: fix csets memory leak in string_utf8_dup

Free csets array when charset conversion loop completes without
finding a valid conversion to prevent memory leak.

Part-of: <https://gitlab.freedesktop.org/gstreamer/gstreamer/-/merge_requests/10017>
---
 gst-libs/gst/tag/id3v2frames.c | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/gst-libs/gst/tag/id3v2frames.c b/gst-libs/gst/tag/id3v2frames.c
index f39659b..4b55fa1 100644
--- a/gst-libs/gst/tag/id3v2frames.c
+++ b/gst-libs/gst/tag/id3v2frames.c
@@ -1051,6 +1051,7 @@ string_utf8_dup (const gchar * start, const guint size)
         utf8 = NULL;
       }
     }
+    g_strfreev (csets);
   }
   /* Try current locale (if not UTF-8) */
   if (!g_get_charset (&env)) {
